project.name: joke_self
project.notes: this is a remake of the original Scratch sample project "joke", using a few of SNAP!'s more advanced features, such as dispatch procedure style OOP to create a simple ReadStream class. Note, since the stream is already initialized in the downloaded project, you don't have to click on the "initialize" hat block. It is just there to show you what needed to be done for this project. Enjoy! -Jens
